      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-8 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
