    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is cooking, rinse the<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it is tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
