    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
