    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until bright green and wilted</p><p>Once the beans are done, squeeze in the<strong> juice</strong> of<strong> 1/2</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> orange</strong> – this is your<strong> black bean stew</strong></p>",
