    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>orange</strong> into wedges and slice the <strong>cooked pork belly</strong> finely</p><p>Serve the<strong> black bean stew</strong> over the<strong> cooked brown rice</strong>, with<strong> wilted greens</strong> and <strong>orange wedges </strong>to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>pork belly slices</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
